<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="enquiry-inquiry-n">enquiry / inquiry <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'kwaɪəri/    美 /'ɪnkwəri ; ɪn'kwaɪəri/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>询问；调查：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Thank you for your <strong>enquiry / enquiries about</strong> my health.
谢谢你询问我的健康状况。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The police have <strong>launched / set up an inquiry into</strong> the accident. 
警方已开始进行事故调查。</p></div></div>